Package: Nessie
Title: Running The Friends-of-Friends Algorithm On Redshift Surveys
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Trystan", "Lambert", , "trystanscottlambert@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This packages runs the Friends-of-Friends algorithm as described in Lambert+2025 (based of the orignal code from Robotham+2011) on a given redshift survey and includes a variety of helper functions to optimize for the best linking length parameters given a mock catalogue, and construct a running density of the survey.
